Requirements:

Tech Stack:

Next.js (latest version, using App Router)

TailwindCSS for styling

TypeScript preferred but optional

Design / Layout:

Match the visual style of BrittanyChiang.com as closely as possible: dark/light mode, accent animations, smooth scrolling, and minimalistic modern look

Responsive for mobile, tablet, and desktop

Include hover/focus animations where appropriate (like link underlines, social icons, skill progress bars, etc.)

Data Model:

All content (name, bio, projects, skills, social links, work experience, education, contact info) should be driven from a JSON file

