Deliverables:

Fully working Next.js + TailwindCSS app

Sample data.json

Optional theme.json

README.md

Minimal placeholder images/icons if needed

Output Format:

Return all code in a format ready to copy into a Next.js project folder structure.

Include comments explaining where to customize components or JSON-driven data.

End Goal:
A highly configurable, JSON-driven resume app that looks visually almost identical to BrittanyChiang.com, ready for deployment, with a thorough README for a senior React developer new to Next.js.

